<center><h1>LOGO-ARCHIVE</h1></center>
<hr noshade width=45%>
<img align=left src="ak10.gif">
<b><font size=4>A</font>ll logo's you find here,
originate in Belgium (our federal occupation power) and
are more or less original. If you can use them for 
whatever purpus, please do and don't bother copywright laws;
we don't play that game, this world belongs to everyone.</b>
<br>
<img align=right src="nar.gif"> 
<b><font size=4>T</font>he quality of the scanned material
is, as you can see yourself, variable. It depends on the fun
we had scanning them. This way you see our own preferences. Not
that we want to push something.</b>
