<DOCHDR>
http://www.knooppunt.be:80/~jesgent/rpage/muzam.htm 194.10.201.200 19970122114531 text/html 1737
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: CERN/3.0
