<H1>Leaves in the wind</H1>
<HR>
<P></P>
<P>Take a dream and watch it scatter<BR>
In the big scene it doesn't matter<BR>
Take a promise watch it break<BR>
After all life's what you make</P>
<P><B>It's all leaves in the wind</B></P>
<P></P>
Take a lie and make it better<BR>
write it down and send a letter<BR>
Take the truth and carefully twist it<BR>
Stare at it long enough untill you've missed it
<P><B>It's all leaves in the wind</B></P>
<P>Everything is like a tree <BR>
rooted down and losing leaves<BR>
everything is broken everything is broken</P>
<P><B>It's all leaves in the wind</B>                    </P>
<P><I>Johan Raedemakers</I></P>
