<HEAD><TITLE>MBJESNL</TITLE></HEAD>


<CENTER><BODY><body bgcolor="#3f363e" text="#ffffff" link="#ffff00" vlink="#80ffff"><center><A HREF="http://www.knooppunt.be/~jesgent/index.htm"><img src="jesdef1.gif"></A><P><font size=8><B>Jeugd en Stad<BR>
<Font size=6>
Brussels, Belgium</B><BR><Font size=4><I>(for an <A HREF="mbjesnl.htm">Dutch</A> version ...)</I><BR></center></B><BR>
<img src="linero2.gif"><BR>
<table><td width="600"><font size=4><BR>
<img src="media1.gif"><BR>

<Font size=4>
<H2>OBJECTIVES</H2>

The development of a vocational training in an area which is attractive to young people. Supporting unemployed youngsters from disadvantaged backgrounds through training and into employment.<BR><BR><BR>


<H2>ACTIVITIES</H2>

The focus is concentrated on the world of audio:<BR><BR>

PART 1 - GENERAL STUDIO TECHNIQUES<BR><BR>

<ul><li>Introduction to sound in its acoustic form
<li>Analog and digital sound
<li>Microphones: types and techniques
<li>Mixing:connections and routing
<li>Equalizing
<li>Effects
<li>Dynamic processors
<li>MIDI
<li>Synchronisation (MTC, SMPTE)<BR><BR></ul>

PART 2 - DIGITAL SOUND RECORDING<BR>

<ul><li>Sampling frequency and quantizing
<li>Sound formats
<li>Sound on the Internet
<li>Sound (waveform) editing
<li>Advanced editing and transformation of sound
<li>Effects and processors on Pro Tools III
<li>Automated mixing
<li>Mastering</ul><BR>


<H2>TARGET GROUP</H2>

Unemployed youngsters aged between 18 and 20 years.<BR><BR><BR>

<H2>CONTACT</H2>

Koen Hanssens<BR>
Tel. 0032 (0)2 411 68 83<BR>
Fax. 0032 (0)2 410 60 43<BR>
mail: <a href="mailto:De.Rockfabriek@ping.be"><i>De.Rockfabriek@ping.be</i></a><BR><BR>
<img src="linero2.gif"><BR><BR>
<Font size=4> <center><a href="mb.htm">The Media Bridge home page</A> (...)   
</center><P>
