<a name="weblinks"></a>
<h1><center>Links to Basque and other Web-Pages</center></h1>
<hr><p>

<img hspace=5 src="/~euskadi/layout/c_green.gif"><font size=4><b>We recommend:</b></font>
<font size=3><ul>
<li><a href="http://weber.u.washington.edu/~buber/basque.html">Buber's Basque Home Page,</a> very good for the basque language and culture.<br>
<br>
</ul></font>
<p>

<img hspace=5 src="/~euskadi/layout/c_green.gif"><font size=4><b>And our special friends:</b></font>
<font size=3><ul>
<li><a href="http://www.music.ch/recrec/agitprop/ng/home.htm">Agitprop</a>, the people who manages NEGU GORRIAK in Germany, Austria and Switzerland.<br>
<li><a href="http://www.serve.com/rm/">Sinn Féin</a>, The Irish Republicans and their weekly magazine 'An Phoblacht'.<br>
<li><a href="http://www.peak.org/~justin/ezln/ezln.html">YA BASTA!</a> - Chiapas: Homepage of the EZLN.<br>
<li><a href="http://www.xs4all.nl/~covert/">Kurdistan</a> Information Center.<br>
</ul></font>
<p>

<img hspace=5 src="/~euskadi/layout/c_green.gif"><font size=4><b>Have a look here, too:</b></font>
<font size=3><ul>
<li><a href="http://www.igc.apc.org/">IGC/APC</a> - The Link to LaborNet, EcoNet, WomansNet etc.<br>
<li>Brush up your basic 
<a href="http://www.idbsu.edu/surveyrc/Staff/jaynes/marxism/marxism.htm">Marxism.</a>
<li>And don't forget <a href="http://tigerden.com/~berios/chomsky.html">Chomsky.</a>
</ul></font>
