<HEAD>
<TITLE>ICYE Europe</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY background="back.jpg">
<H1><CENTER>Welcome</CENTER></H1>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="why.gif"></CENTER>
<P>Welcome to the ICYE Europe homepage.  We are an international <STRONG>youth exchange</STRONG> organisation, and we focus on <STRONG>volunteering</STRONG>.<BR>
This is the first update of our page so excuse us for all the little mistakes.<BR>
In this site you can find information about the ICYE Federation and ICYE Europe.  You can find adresses, phone numbers, fax numbers, 
... from all our members, friends, platforms we work with.  As if this is not yet enough, you can also find upcoming activities with an application form, pictures, and links to websites about youth topics.<BR>
</P>
<P><STRONG>So if you think this is cool, groovy, or just usefull, just <A HREF="icye.htm">ENTER</A>, and maybe you 'll find out "WHY ?".</STRONG></P>
<HR>
<CENTER><EM>Designed by Hans Langouche<BR>
<A HREF="mailto:kurdy@dds.nl">kurdy@dds.nl</A></EM></CENTER>
</BODY>
