<HEAD>
<TITLE>ICYE Europe</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY  BACKGROUND="back.jpg">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="x.gif" BORDER=0 = ALT="[icye logo]"></CENTER>
<P>
</P>
<HR>
<P><STRONG>ICYE is an international non-governemental organisation founded in 1949 to
contribute, through one-year youth exchanges, to initiatives for peace and reconciliation among
the peoples involved in World War II.</STRONG></P>
<HR>
<H1>ICYE Europe</H1>
<UL>
<LI><H2><A HREF="feder.htm">The ICYE Federation</A></H2>
