<h1>SAMPLE CD's</h1>
<hr>
We are one of the few music-stores in Belgium that store a wide range of sample-CD's.<br>
We try to keep a large collection of popular CD's in our juke-box, so that customers can try the CD's before buying them.
<p>
All titles are stocked in plain audio-CD-format.<br>
The numbers are the corresponding numbers on our jukebox.<br>
<b>Prices given apply only to the audio-format.</b><br>
Most of the CD's can be acquired in sampler-specific CD-ROM-format.<br>
