Subject: OMCT/COL29056/VIOLENCE/AGAINST/CUT/
Date: 30 May 1996 02:19:47

Subject: OMCT/COL29056/VIOLENCE/AGAINST/CUT/MEMBERS/COLOMBIA

--=====================_833466299==_
Content-Type: text/plain; charset="us-ascii"



--=====================_833466299==_
Content-Type: text/plain; charset="iso-8859-1"
