Subject: Earth Council/Habitat II Report
Date: 04 Jun 1996 09:47:55 -0800 (PST)

The Earth Council is pleased to present the
report "Human Settlements: People Making a
Difference" in preparation for the Second
United Nations Conference on Human
Settlements (Habitat II).  The report was
prepared in collaboration with the Habitat
International Coalition (HIC), the
International Council for Local
Environmental Initiatives (ICLEI), the
Caucus of Development NGO Networks of the
Philippines (CODE-NGO), and the
International Federation of the Red Cross
and Red Crescent Societies.

The report is now available in print, on
diskette in hypertext format, and on the
Earth Council's World Wide Web server
(<a href=http://www.ecouncil.ac.cr)>http://www.ecouncil.ac.cr)</a>

For more information about this and other
Earth Council projects, please visit our
homepage or contact us directly at:

     Earth Council
     Apartado 2323-1002
     San Jose, Costa Rica

     ph: +506-256-1611
     fx: +506-255-2197
     e-mail: eci@terra.ecouncil.ac.cr /     
     ecouncil@igc.apc.org

Sincerely,

Kevin Hudgins
Information System
