<a name=L10000></a><a href=#L10001>So</a>: U-af
From: omct@iprolink.ch
Newsgroups: africa.horn
Subject: OMCTFI:SDN06056/arbitrary arrests
Date: 30 May 1996 03:45:25

--=====================_833470570==_
Content-Type: text/plain; charset="us-ascii"



--=====================_833470570==_
